  "remarks": "Vadzim Mazol is a Belarusian judge of the Pruzhany District Court of the Brest Region. He was appointed by Aliaksandr Lukashenka. He issued sentences against a large number of citizens of Belarus who voiced their opinions against the President and the regime’s law enforcement authorities, including on social media.",
